EN: His desk always remains clean and tidy.

ZH: 她喜欢用干净的毛巾擦脸。
EN: She likes to wipe her face with a clean towel.

ZH: 这些碗盘非常干净，可以直接使用。
EN: These plates and bowls are very clean and can be used directly.

ZH: 我的手很干净，你可以和我握手。
EN: My hands are clean, you can shake hands with me.

ZH: 这家餐厅很干净，我经常来吃饭。
EN: This restaurant is very clean, I often eat here.

ZH: 我刚刚洗完澡，身体很干净。
EN: I just finished taking a shower, my body is clean.

