EN: The hotel's kitchen is very clean and hygienic.

ZH: 她的笑容洁白而干净。
EN: Her smile is bright and clean.

ZH: 这个水果市场卖的水果都很新鲜干净。
EN: The fruits sold at this market are fresh and clean.

ZH: 她擦地擦得很干净，一尘不染。
EN: She cleaned the floor very clean, without a speck of dust.

ZH: 这个学校的教室都很干净整洁。
EN: The classrooms in this school are clean and tidy.

ZH: 她的指甲很干净，修剪得很整齐。
EN: Her nails are clean and neatly trimmed.

ZH: 这个公园的景色很干净清新。
EN: The scenery in this park is clean and fresh.

ZH: 他洗衣服的时候，总是把它们洗得很干净。
EN: When he washes clothes, he always cleans them very well.

ZH: 这间宾馆打扫得非常干净，服务也很好。
EN: This hotel is cleaned very well and the service is also good.

ZH: 奶奶一直教育我们保持环境干净整洁。
EN: Grandma has always taught us to keep the environment clean and tidy.

ZH: 她的手写字很干净工整。
EN: Her handwriting is very clean and neat.

ZH: 这个国家的街道都很干净。
EN: The streets in this country are very clean.

ZH: 这个湖的水非常干净透明。
EN: The water in this lake is very clean and transparent.
